title: Ep 105 - How to Get Out of A Rut
itunes:title: Ep 105 - How to Get Out of A Rut
description:
As humans, we all get in ruts. We all have days where we are completely unmotivated and don't want to put in any work. In this episode I give my top 3 tips to getting yourself out of a rut.
